schools.name: Major Cheney El At South Birdville

data.description: This beautiful home is awaiting you!  It has been fully renovated inside and out.  It has 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The primary bedroom is oversized with a beautiful full-sized bath.  The open floor plan is perfect for family and gatherings and has plenty of natural light.  Plenty of cabinet space in the kitchen. The huge backyard is perfect for playing outside and gathering with friends and family.  In 2021 new stove and dishwasher were installed, as well as a new HVAC and water heater. The plumbing and electrical have also been updated.  Close proximity to Downtown and mid-cities.  Easy access to 121.
